if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_skuattention')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_skuattention
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_skuattention */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_skuattention (
ID int identity(100000,1),
SkuID int not null,
AdminID int null,
constraint PK_BUSI_SKUATTENTION primary key (ID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_skuattention') and minor_id = 0)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'基础-关注sku(OK)',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_skuattention')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'ID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention', 'column', 'ID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'ID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention', 'column', 'ID'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_skuattention')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'SkuID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention', 'column', 'SkuID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'SKUID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention', 'column', 'SkuID'
go

if exists(select 1 from sys.extended_properties p where
p.major_id = object_id('busi_skuattention')
and p.minor_id = (select c.column_id from sys.columns c where c.object_id = p.major_id and c.name = 'AdminID')
)
begin
declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_dropextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention', 'column', 'AdminID'

end


select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'管理员ID',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_skuattention', 'column', 'AdminID'
go
